OL,3,C'Does the police lie?' - Officers
OL,4,Cgiven scripted answers after Maccabi
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police staff appear to
OL,8,Fhave been given a script and model
OL,9,Fanswers to some questions people might
OL,10,Fask about the controversial Maccabi
OL,11,Ffan ban and the position of the chief
OL,12,Fconstable.
OL,14,FA document sent to officers and seen
OL,15,Fby ITV News Central show questions
OL,16,Flike: Was the force wrong to ban
OL,17,FMaccabi Tel Aviv fans? Do you think
OL,18,Fthe chief constable should be sacked?
OL,19,FDoes the force regularly lie? And, is
OL,20,Fthe police force racist?
