OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FGovernment ministers, including the
OL,8,FHome Secretary and Health Secretary,
OL,9,Fare calling for Chief Constable Craig
OL,10,FGuildford to be sacked.
OL,12,FIt comes after a highly critical
OL,13,Freview into how his force handled the
OL,14,Fdecision to ban Maccabi Tel Aviv fans
OL,15,Ffrom a Europa League game at Aston
OL,16,FVilla last November. Guildford had
OL,17,Falso admitted errors in evidence,
OL,18,Fcaused by using AI.
