OL,3,C'Does the police lie?' - Officers
OL,4,Cgiven scripted answers after Maccabi
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FAmid the furore, it seems West
OL,8,FMidlands Police staff are being
OL,9,Fencouraged to stick to "key messages"
OL,10,Fto "minimise negative community
OL,11,Fimpact, rebuild public and partner
OL,12,Ftrust and confidence, and maintain
OL,13,Feffective policing services".
OL,15,FThe document listed possible questions
OL,16,Fofficers may receive from members of
OL,17,Fthe public, including: "Were West
OL,18,FMidlands Police wrong to ban Maccabi
OL,19,FTel Aviv fans?"
