OL,3,C'Does the police lie?' - Officers
OL,4,Cgiven scripted answers after Maccabi
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FAn example response read: "I can't
OL,8,Fcomment further than the statement
OL,9,Fwhich has been issued on behalf of the
OL,10,Fforce. As a serving member of WMP, my
OL,11,Ffocus, alongside colleagues, is on
OL,12,Fkeeping our communities safe and
OL,13,Ftackling crime."
OL,15,FThe document also includes the
OL,16,Fquestion: "Do you think the Chief
OL,17,FConstable should be sacked? Have you
OL,18,Flost confidence in him too?"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
