OL,3,C'Does the police lie?' - Officers
OL,4,Cgiven scripted answers after Maccabi
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FThe proposed answer read: "It would be
OL,8,Finappropriate and unprofessional to
OL,9,Fdiscuss the future of anyone else
OL,10,Fwithin the organisation."
OL,12,FAnother possible question was: "Can we
OL,13,Ftrust you? Does WMP regularly lie?"
OL,15,FWith the proposed answer: "We're here
OL,16,Fto help you. It's through working with
OL,17,Fyou that we continue to make our
OL,18,Fcommunities safer. Your information
OL,19,Fregularly helps to ensure we can take
OL,20,Faction to resolve matters which matter
OL,21,Fto you."
