OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FThe briefing document also includes a
OL,8,Flist of key messages to the public,
OL,9,Fincluding the statement: "We are
OL,10,Fextremely sorry for the impact these
OL,11,Fmatters have had on individuals and
OL,12,Ftheir communities."
OL,14,FAsked about the document, West
OL,15,FMidlands Police told ITV News Central:
OL,16,F"We regularly provide our frontline
OL,17,Fofficers and staff, who are
OL,18,Fcommunicating all the time with
OL,19,Fmembers of the community, with
OL,20,Finformation that may assist them with
OL,21,Fthese conversations."
